headline: Johnson & Johnson to showcase industry-leading neuropsychiatry innovations at the 2025 Psych Congress Annual Meeting
summary: Johnson & Johnson (NYSE: JNJ) announced today that 21 abstracts featuring new real-world and clinical trial data will be presented at the annual U.S. Psychiatric and Mental Health Congress (Psych Congress), taking place September 17 to 21 in San Diego, California. Presentations include the latest research from across the Company's neuropsychiatry portfolio, including major depressive disorder (MDD), treatment-resistant depression (TRD) and schizophrenia.
